{"tid":682413,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"最近連登仔係咪又低質左","createTime":"2018-05-29T00:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T01:16:29.000Z","uid":118463,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"805afd6e66ef0bd9d85537d3e051199b015a5dc9","tid":682413,"uid":118463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T00:29:24.000Z","msg":"呢排睇10個po<br />\n有9個一入去就會見到有人覆 關你鬼事咩<br />\n仲要一堆人正評<br />\n結果咪又係比人串番 樓主個po唔關樓主事 咁樓主開po又關佢咩事<br />\n討論區就一定要講關自己事既野？<br />\n咁班窮撚就算d樓再平 咪又係買唔起  咁係咪大家都唔洗理？<br />\n串串貢以為自己好型<br />\n班中學生岩畢業就咁快上到黎架？"},{"pid":"9bebb47d80b11a6371a78b73ba97d7f8a058eb96","tid":682413,"uid":187723,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T01:11:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b42b271bd8dbfbd882e9c1531bdde5ab89fb83df","tid":682413,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T01:19:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"330c75c3173ad6937a363c24b4a83cfd38a0b178","tid":682413,"uid":135083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T19:59:38.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係成班小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e6787d20651d38ef7a84b6f0486b7a3ad179e8","tid":682413,"uid":173852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T23:19:52.000Z","msg":"我會答係<br />\n<br />\n幾個月前d膠論都係有 但好似無咁多 無乜人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 基本上可以無視，簡d高質topic傾<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪因為暑假，近排日日上黎成版都係父幹，公屋post，而且好撚多傻仔跟住一齊附和、叫春。<br />\n<br />\n之前都有心想討論下，而家真係勿認真算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36cd4e6827a64ddc45f3ee95c2e497e9ae9c91ee","tid":682413,"uid":115535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T23:38:12.000Z","msg":"多得d中學雞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6b3da744ca8c1